response.original_title: 200GANA-1460 ナイトプールナンパ 01 (森川アンナ) アンナ 28歳 スキューバのインストラクター
response.overview: Anna said that she came alone when she finally talked to a woman in the night pool saying "Can I pick you up ?!" It's a beautiful adult woman and her swimsuit is very nice! !! Anna said, "Let's drink only one cup! Let's go play!" And reluctantly followed us to the room. Anna fell asleep because she was so excited when she talked while drinking alcohol. Now it's our turn from here. The good thing about getting drunk and sleeping is to take off your clothes and bra.
response.title: 200GANA-1460 Night Pool Pickup 01 (Morikawa Anna) Anna, 28 years old, scuba instructor
